GIT Assignment

git status - It shows what is the current status of the project.

git clone url - It copies the entire project which is on the GITHub to your local

To push a file to GitHub steps
create a repo in Github
create a file in VScode
git add file_name
git commit -m "message"
git push origin main

To Push a project to GitHub steps
create a repo in Github
open the project in VScode
git init
git remote add origin url
git add .
git commit -m "message"
git push origin main

To create the Branch of a repo steps
open a folder in VScode
git clone url
cd filename
git checkout -b branch_name
git add .
git commit -m "message"
git push origin branch_name

To merge with branch
git checkout branch_name
git merge main
git add .
git commit -m "message"
git push origin branch_name

The reset commands
git reset head~1 - it will reset the branch to previous commit
git reset --hard - it will reset to previous commit
